    "en": {
      "title": "Community Kitchen hosted by Rotary Club of Colombo Mid Town and Meal Care",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Rotary Club of Colombo Mid Town, together with Meal Care, recently distributed 400 lunch packs amongst the community in Rajaguru Sri Subuthi Road and Veluwanarama Road in Wellawatta. Beneficiaries of the project included economically deprived families who are affected by the current economic crisis. Rotarians and their families from the Rotary Club of Colombo Mid Town and volunteers from Meal Care participated in the distribution with the aim of uplifting the community during this challenging time period. The project was funded by attune Lanka Ltd. and the well-wishers."
      ],
